            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1675785361319-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut a large piece of <strong>tin foil</strong> and place it on a baking tray</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Place your <strong>smoked</strong> <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> in the centre of the foil</p><p>Top each basa fillet with a small knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1675785377953-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
