            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1675785377953-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Scrunch the edges of the foil together around the fish to form a tightly sealed parcel[s]</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 12-15 min or until the fish is cooked through (keep the basa in the foil parcels until ready to serve!)</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1675785394722-x200.jpg",
