    {
      "instruction": "<p>Bring the reserved pot with plenty of<strong> boiled water</strong> to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Crack your<strong> egg[s] </strong>gently into the water and leave for 3 min</p><p>Once done, gently transfer the <strong>egg[s] </strong>with a slotted spoon to<strong> </strong>kitchen paper or a clean tea-towel – this is your <strong>poached egg[s]</strong></p>",
